{"tid":463942,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"其實係咪大部分人都唔知自己想做咩，只係見步行步？","createTime":"2017-11-10T04:21:25.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-11T16:29:21.000Z","uid":101687,"like":34,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"1b6e97c236f56c6b97e1b1d6651c55ed143fc985","tid":463942,"uid":101687,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-10T04:21:25.000Z","msg":"出左黎做野幾年..第一次轉工<br />\n其實都唔係好知自己想搵份咩工 下次再轉要點點點<br />\n只係想轉下 人工跳得快d<br />\n個人又冇乜特別興趣 好似做乜都唔會特別開心咁<br />\n最想都係打份hea工 人工唔太低就ok<br />\n<br />\n其實大部分人都係類似想法 定其實個個都好有目標<br />\n我會係度諗係咪成功既年諗野唔會好似我咁<br />\n係會一早計劃好哂自己條路要點行<br />\n定其實佢地都只係跟住際遇行<br />\n咁岩有機會就上到位 做到老細"},{"pid":"7958ddd3eeb23f333f3831a3c087a4a0d2b41516","tid":463942,"uid":101687,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-10T05:04:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"88894f78b5f7a368a7ddc232801fe473487c72e2","tid":463942,"uid":54387,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-10T06:28:49.000Z","msg":"就嚟退休都唔知自己想做乜"},{"pid":"d7d66a53464458538d26a419c6251ee2ea76c2bc","tid":463942,"uid":151877,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-10T07:04:54.000Z","msg":"退埋休都唔知自己做緊咩 有孫就湊住先 都係見步行步 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0a21a0ad37d9cf5ce44bec193e10c322202a7082","tid":463942,"uid":129509,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-10T07:06:19.000Z","msg":"由中五開始已經有哂目標<br />\n一直進發緊 做到自己想做既野其實真係好開心"},{"pid":"1105f658443a9733f77731c816589b0d41bdb7a7","tid":463942,"uid":76632,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-10T07:24:04.000Z","msg":"想做軍人或特工之類，但唔想入警隊或入解放軍。目前打下雜工，教下拳<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"55dbfccce0d9d63e97ee9a93b3ef71a432fdc229","tid":463942,"uid":129509,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-10T07:35:29.000Z","msg"